  "texts": [
    "This manager evaluated requests and performed many important tasks such as validation, encryption, and data loading.",
    "Similarly, in another study [12] an entity called the authenticator evaluated and validated requests.",
    "Consequently, in these proposed schemes, the EHR manager and the authenticator were vulnerable to attacks.In study [6], although the patient medical data were stored on the cloud server, only the indices of these data were kept in the blockchain.",
    "The study included a system administrator group consisting of government medical institutions and managers of hospitals.",
    "This group was given the authority to authorize many actions including user registration, authentication, and system control."
  ]
}